               <msContents>
                  <summary>Anaphora of Our Lady Mary attributed to Cyriacus of Bǝhǝnsa, ቅዳሴ፡ ማርያም፡; Prayer of the Covenant, ጸሎተ፡ ኪዳን፡.</summary>
